{
  "text": "We first show that W n defined in (43) indeed satisfies the recursive equations [CITATION_1] , that is we prove the existence part of Theorem 1(a). 1) Existence: Proof. [Proof of Theorem 1(a); existence]Introduce the truncation of H \u2212\u221e,n defined by deleting the rightmost non-zero column,",
